  "title": "Smoky Roasted Uruguayan Chicken Stir-fry",
  "description": "This low-carb-friendly smoky roasted Uruguayan chicken stir-fry is tender and comforting, featuring orange blossom water for added flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
