      "amount": "3-4 sprigs"
    },
    {
      "name": "Garlic Cloves",
      "amount": "6 cloves"
    },
    {
      "name": "Olive Oil",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "Salt and Black Pepper",
      "amount": "to taste"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a small bowl, mix Orange Blossom Water, Soy Sauce, Brown Sugar, Thyme Sprigs, Garlic Cloves, Olive Oil, Salt, and Black Pepper.",
    "Place Urkund Chicken Breasts on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper. Drizzle the marinade mixture evenly over each piece of chicken.",
    "Roast in preheated oven for 25-30 minutes or until internal temperature reaches 165°F (74°C).",
    "Remove from oven and let rest for 5 minutes before slicing.",
    "Serve hot with your favorite side dishes."
  ],
